ns0:svg.ns0:text: Look carefully at the image showing Elements of the weather. Identify the different parts and think about what they represent. Use your observations to answer the questions that follow.
1. What are the main things you see in the picture related to the weather?
2. Can you point out and name the different elements shown in the illustration that help us understand the weather?
3. What do you think the image is trying to tell us about the different types of weather?
4. How do you think the elements shown in the picture affect our daily lives or activities?
5. If you were to add one more element to the illustration to make it more complete, what would it be and why?
